# Variables — pega aqui el token que devuelve POST /api/auth/login
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

###

### Obtener Usuarios
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gestion
Accept: application/json

### Obtener nacionalidades
GET http://localhost:8080/api/nacionalidad/
Accept: application/json

### Agregar una Nacionalidad
POST http://localhost:8080/api/nacionalidad
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pais": "Bolivia",
  "estado": true
}

### Editar una nacionalidad
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/nacionalidad/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pais": "Bolivia"
}

### Eliminar logicamente una nacionalidad
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/nacionalidad/3
Accept: application/json


###Get by id nacionalidad
GET http://localhost:8080/nacionalidad/getbyId
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


{
  "id":6
}

###Get by id nacionalidad Param
GET http://localhost:8080/nacionalidad/getbyId/5
Accept: application/json


### Crear Persona + Usuario (transaccion atomica)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/usuario/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "persona": {
    "nombre": "Javier",
    "ci": "71506101",
    "genero": "masculino",
    "fnac": "10/07/1993",
    "ap": "Alcoba",
    "am": "Gutierrez",
    "id_nacionalidad": 1
  },
  "usuario": {
    "email": "javier@dotset.com",
    "password": "Secreta12345",
    "rol": "admin"
  }
}





### Auth
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "javier@gmail.com",
  "password": "Contrasena12345"
}